It is the 35th combination in the Sexagenary cycle; the preceding combination is {{ill|Dingyou|ja|丁酉}} and the following combination is {{ill|Jihai|ja|己亥}}. In the system of {{ill|Yin-Yang and the Five Elements|ja|陰陽五行思想|lt=Yin-Yang Five Elements|lt_ja=陰陽五行}}, the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|lt=Ten Heavenly Stems|ja|十干}}’ {{ill|Wu|ja|戊}} represents yang {{ill|Earth|ja|土}}, while the {{ill|Twelve Earthly Branches|ja|十二支}}’ {{ill|Dog|ja|戌}} also represents yang {{ill|Earth|ja|土}}, and together they exhibit a relationship of {{ill|Biwa (Mutual Harmony)|ja|五行思想#比和（ひわ）|lt=Biwa|lt_ja=比和}}.

== Years of Wuxu ==
A year in the {{ill|Common Era|ja|西暦}} that leaves a remainder of 38 when divided by 60 is a {{ill|Year|ja|年}} of Wuxu.
