{{infobox Chinese|l=Yang Earth Dog|kanji=戊戌|romaji=tsuchinoe inu|onyomi=bojutsu|p=wùxū|w=wu-hsü|mi=u⁵⁵ ɕy|y=mou6 seot1|j=mou6 seot1|ci=mɐu sœt̚|mc=məu syt|oc-bs=mə ssu}}
{{Sexagenary cycle comprehensive}}
'''Yang Earth Dog also known as <!--please transliterate all the hiragana readings into romaji and provide the kanji--> 戊戌''' (つちのえいぬ、ぼどのいぬ、ぼじゅつ) is one of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|干支|12=draft|12=draft}}.

It is the 35th combination in the Sexagenary cycle; the preceding combination is {{ill|Dingyou|ja|丁酉|12=draft|12=draft}} and the following combination is {{ill|Jihai|ja|己亥|12=draft|12=draft}}. In the system of {{ill|Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|ja|陰陽五行思想|lt=Yin-Yang Five Elements|lt_ja=陰陽五行|12=draft|12=draft}}, the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|lt=Ten Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|12=draft|12=draft}}’ {{ill|Wu|ja|戊|1=Tsuchinoe (戊)|12=draft|12=draft}} represents yang {{ill|Earth|ja|土|12=draft|12=draft}}, while the {{ill|Twelve Earthly Branches|ja|十二支|12=draft|12=draft}}’ {{ill|Dog|ja|戌|1=Dog (zodiac)|lt=Dog (戌)|12=draft|12=draft}} also represents yang {{ill|Earth|ja|土|12=draft|12=draft}}, and together they exhibit a relationship of {{ill|Biwa (Mutual Harmony)|ja|五行思想#比和（ひわ）|lt=Biwa|lt_ja=比和|12=draft|12=draft}}.

== Years of Wuxu ==
A year in the {{ill|Common Era|ja|西暦|12=draft|12=draft}} that leaves a remainder of 38 when divided by 60 is a {{ill|Year|ja|年|12=draft|12=draft}} of Wuxu.
