{{Sexagenary cycle comprehensive}}
'''Yang Earth Dog also known as  戊戌''' (つちのえいぬ、ぼどのいぬ、ぼじゅつ) is one of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|干支|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}.

It is the 35th combination in the Sexagenary cycle; the preceding combination is {{ill|Dingyou|ja|丁酉|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} and the following combination is {{ill|Jihai|ja|己亥|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. In the system of {{ill|Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|ja|陰陽五行思想|lt=Yin-Yang Five Elements|lt_ja=陰陽五行|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|lt=Ten Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}’ {{ill|Wu|ja|戊|1=Tsuchinoe (戊)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} represents yang {{ill|Earth|ja|土|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, while the {{ill|Twelve Earthly Branches|ja|十二支|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}’ {{ill|Dog|ja|戌|1=Dog (zodiac)|lt=Dog (戌)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} also represents yang {{ill|Earth|ja|土|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, and together they exhibit a relationship of {{ill|Biwa (Mutual Harmony)|ja|五行思想#比和（ひわ）|lt=Biwa|lt_ja=比和|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}.

