{{infobox Chinese|l=Yang Earth Dog|kanji=戊戌|romaji=tsuchinoe inu|onyomi=bojutsu|p=wùxū|w=wu-hsü|mi=u⁵⁵ ɕy|y=mou6 seot1|j=mou6 seot1|ci=mɐu sœt̚|mc=məu syt|oc-bs=mə ssu|qq=}}
{{Sexagenary cycle comprehensive|qq=}}
'''Yang Earth Dog also known as  戊戌''' (つちのえいぬ、ぼどのいぬ、ぼじゅつ) is one of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|干支|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|qq=}}.

It is the 35th combination in the Sexagenary cycle; the preceding combination is {{ill|Dingyou|ja|丁酉|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Dingyou|qq=}} and the following combination is {{ill|Jihai|ja|己亥|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jihai|qq=}}. In the system of {{ill|Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|ja|陰陽五行思想|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|lt=Yin-Yang Five Elements|lt_ja=陰陽五行|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=}}, the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|lt=Ten Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stems|qq=}}’ {{ill|Wu|ja|戊|1=Tsuchinoe (戊)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wu|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsuchinoe (戊)|qq=}} represents yang {{ill|Earth|ja|土|1=Earth (wuxing)|lt=Earth (土)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Earth|qq=}}, while the {{ill|Twelve Earthly Branches|1=Earthly Branches|lt=Twelve Earthly Branches|ja|十二支|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Twelve Earthly Branches|13=User:Immanuelle/Earthly Branches|qq=}}’ {{ill|Dog|ja|戌|1=Dog (zodiac)|lt=Dog (戌)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Dog|13=User:Immanuelle/Dog (zodiac)|qq=}} also represents yang {{ill|Earth|ja|土|1=Earth (wuxing)|lt=Earth (土)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Earth|qq=}}, and together they exhibit a relationship of {{ill|Biwa (Mutual Harmony)|ja|五行思想#比和（ひわ）|1=比和|1=Wuxing (Chinese philosophy)#Harmonious Relationship (比和)|2=ja|3=五行思想#比和（ひわ）|lt=Harmonious Relationship (Five Elements)|qq=Biwa|lt_ja=比和|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Biwa (Mutual Harmony)|13=User:Immanuelle/比和|qq=}}.

