--> ==Years of Yang Earth Dog== A year in the [[:en:Common Era|Common Era]] that leaves a remainder of 38 when divided by 60 is a [[:en:Year|Year]] of Wuxu. {| class="wikitable" |+ '''Years of Wuxu''' |- ! [[:en:1st millennium|1st Millennium]] !! [[:en:2nd millennium|2nd Millennium]] !! [[:en:3rd millennium|3rd Millennium]] |- | * [[:en:AD 38|38 AD]] * [[:en:AD 98|98 AD]] * [[:en:158|158 AD]] * [[:en:218|218 AD]] * [[:en:278|278 AD]] * [[:en:338|338 AD]] * [[:en:398|398 AD]] * [[:en:458|458 AD]] * [[:en:518|518 AD]] * [[:en:578|578 AD]] * [[:en:638|638 AD]] * [[:en:698|698 AD]] * [[:en:758|758 AD]] * [[:en:818|818 AD]] * [[:en:878|878 AD]] * [[:en:938|938 AD]] * [[:en:998|998 AD]] | * [[:en:1058|1058 AD]] * [[:en:1118|1118 AD]] * [[:en:1178|1178 AD]] * [[:en:1238|1238 AD]] * [[:en:1298|1298 AD]] * [[:en:1358|1358 AD]] * [[:en:1418|1418 AD]] * [[:en:1478|1478 AD]] * [[:en:1538|1538 AD]] * [[:en:1598|1598 AD]] * [[:en:1658|1658 AD]] * [[:en:1718|1718 AD]] * [[:en:1778|1778 AD]] * [[:en:1838|1838 AD]] * [[:en:1898|1898 AD]] * [[:en:1958|1958 AD]] | * [[:en:2018|2018 AD]] * {{ill|2078 AD|ja|2078年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2078|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2078 AD|qq=|ja_comment=fixed jawiki redirect|3=2070年代|comment=enwiki is a redirect}} * {{ill|2138 AD|ja|2138年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2138|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2138 AD|qq=|ja_comment=fixed jawiki redirect|3=22世紀}} * {{ill|2198 AD|ja|2198年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2198|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2198 AD|qq=|ja_comment=fixed jawiki redirect|3=22世紀}} * {{ill|2258 AD|ja|2258年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2258|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2258 AD|qq=|ja_comment=fixed jawiki redirect|3=23世紀}} * {{ill|2318 AD|ja|2318年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2318|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2318 AD|qq=|ja_comment=fixed jawiki redirect|3=24世紀}} * {{ill|2378 AD|ja|2378年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2378|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2378 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * {{ill|2438 AD|ja|2438年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2438|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2438 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * {{ill|2498 AD|ja|2498年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2498|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2498 AD|qq=|ja_comment=fixed jawiki redirect|3=25世紀}} * {{ill|2558 AD|ja|2558年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2558|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2558 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * {{ill|2618 AD|ja|2618年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2618|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2618 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * {{ill|2678 AD|ja|2678年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2678|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2678 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * {{ill|2738 AD|ja|2738年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2738|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2738 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * {{ill|2798 AD|ja|2798年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2798|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2798 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * {{ill|2858 AD|ja|2858年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2858|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2858 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * {{ill|2918 AD|ja|2918年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2918|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2918 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * {{ill|2978 AD|ja|2978年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2978|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2978 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} |}
=== Events === * In the 9th year of [[:en:Tenpō|Tenpō]] ([[:en:1838|1838 AD]]), [[:en:Takano Chōei|Kōya Nagahide]] authored the work {{ill|Wuxu Dream Tale|ja|戊戌夢物語|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wuxu Dream Tale|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wuxu Dream Tale|qq=}}. * In the 24th year of {{ill|Guangxu|ja|光緒|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Guangxu|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Guangxu|qq=}} ([[:en:1898|1898 AD]]), during the Qing dynasty, reforms and political upheaval known as the [[:en:Hundred Days' Reform|Wuxu Reform]] and the {{ill|Wuxu Coup|ja|戊戌の政変|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wuxu Coup|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Wuxu Coup|qq=|ja_comment=fixed jawiki redirect|3=戊戌の変法}} took place. ==Months of Yang Earth Dog== In a [[:en:Common Era|Common Era]] year whose final digit is 1 or 6 (i.e. when the Ten Heavenly Stems are {{ill|Xin|ja|辛|1=Kanoto (辛)|lt=Kanoto (辛)|2=ja|3=辛|4=zh|5=辛|1=Kanoto (辛)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Xin|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanoto (辛)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Xin|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanoto (辛)|qq=}} or {{ill|Bing|ja|丙|1=Hinoe (丙)|lt=Hinoe (丙)|2=ja|3=丙|4=zh|5=丙|1=Hinoe (丙)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bing|13=User:Immanuelle/Hinoe (丙)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Bing|13=User:Immanuelle/Hinoe (丙)|qq=}}), the month of [[:en:September|September]] becomes the [[:en:Month|Month]] of Wuxu. However, the term “month” here may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} or to a seasonal month (from [[:en:Hanlu|Hanro]] until the day before [[:en:Lidong|Rittō]]) as applicable. ==Days of Yang Earth Dog== The {{ill|Day Selection|ja|選日|1=Senjitsu|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Day Selection|13=User:Immanuelle/Senjitsu|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Day Selection|13=User:Immanuelle/Senjitsu|qq=}} for a Wuxu day is as follows. === Day Selection === A Wuxu day is the 6th day of {{ill|Ten Heaven, One Heaven|ja|天一天上|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ten Heaven, One Heaven|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ten Heaven, One Heaven|qq=|ja_comment=天一神|1=Tenitsu-shin|2=ja|3=天一神}}. == See Also == * {{prefix|qq=}} * {{intitle|qq=}}
